 72.9015, 72.6215, 70.1975, 70.2654, 69.5431, 70.1129, 68.8061, 68.5461, 70.2737, 69.4771, 70.9219, 70.3041, 70.644, 70.5592, 69.2278, 69.0518, 70.4706, 69.924, 69.9773, 70.6461, 67.8955, 64.769, 69.4407, 68.7409, 68.5709, 68.0115, 66.8591, 67.6723, 67.7999, 68.0979, 70.4017, 71.1924, 71.8226, 70.8509, 73.1471, 72.7927, 74.0971, 72.7293, 73.0066, 73.75, 75.6631, 76.808, 77.426, 78.8131, 78.1542, 77.141, 74.4598, 73.637, 73.8378, 73.0168, 73.5963, 73.4862, 74.0622, 74.3771, 75.7159, 74.8269, 74.4419, 74.4199, 74.9707, 75.8806, 77.0538, 77.2227, 77.6301, 78.5385, 81.0272, 80.5594, 81.6456, 81.6208, 82.6702, 83.497, 82.5511, 80.443, 79.9055, 79.0105, 78.6629, 78.909, 77.4966, 77.3978, 77.5738, 77.7912, 77.0838, 76.5174, 76.2119, 76.9068, 76.405, 75.9252, 74.8752, 75.3465, 75.971, 75.8555, 74.8243, 73.449, 72.9304, 70.8185, 72.4594, 73.3625, 72.9837, 74.6406, 75.3818, 76.1643, 75.7347, 75.3135, 75.8957, 75.6989, 73.8961, 71.907, 72.3448, 74.3894, 73.7385, 72.4436, 72.9454, 73.3998, 75.4108, 76.2865, 76.379, 75.4977, 76.6646, 76.401, 76.4041, 76.6775, 76.4896, 76.53, 76.3321, 75.2262, 74.418, 75.1986, 76.7766, 75.7709, 75.3196, 75.4075, 73.1125, 72.5324, 72.74, 72.403, 70.6254, 67.0835, 66.9086, 69.5157, 69.1931, 69.2731, 67.6417, 60.1399, 57.7483, 56.4902, 54.8795, 51.9678, 51.9443, 51.5427, 48.8703, 48.4527, 51.4116, 53.8625, 55.7708, 56.1609, 57.6311, 57.9918, 58.0675, 57.475, 57.6926, 57.3261, 58.0233, 58.8857, 60.1026, 58.7346, 58.1101, 57.2839, 56.9676, 56.4222, 57.2526, 57.9848, 57.253, 55.7112, 56.195, 57.4616, 58.0058, 57.6738, 57.5086, 58.3847, 58.1527, 58.8497, 59.0493, 59.7473, 60.8432, 60.0279, 58.4659, 57.8204, 57.4718, 57.2209, 55.6083, 55.4436, 54.9935, 54.2852, 54.5871, 56.9189, 59.1593, 59.6904, 59.1011, 59.8387, 61.1838, 61.5677, 62.1326, 60.8498, 58.1232, 58.6038, 61.1086, 61.6463, 59.5429, 56.8065, 56.5351, 54.1995, 54.0734, 57.4488, 56.8631, 56.0941, 54.7516, 55.9913, 53.7197, 53.5656, 52.2245, 51.8617, 52.3489, 54.8501, 55.9158, 53.4753, 52.3042, 55.9513, 55.2203, 53.873, 53.2971, 53.7268, 54.3125, 53.9661, 52.4738, 52.2393, 53.1896, 52.9116, 53.5272, 54.9596, 54.0359, 53.1622, 53.766, 53.4824, 54.1569, 55.3523, 56.0371, 55.2182, 56.3351, 57.3881, 56.2169, 54.6002, 55.796, 55.5505, 54.5451], "summary_html": "<h1>高频量价关系因子 (adj_CORA_R)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>从分钟K线计算日内\"价在量先\"错期相关因子（adj_CORA_R），衡量每个品种在分钟频率上绝对收益率领先标准化成交额的协同运动强度。因子值越高，表示该品种的价格波动能引发后续交易量异常放大，反映短期交易过热/投机属性。因子方向为负向（低因子值 = 交易平稳 = 做多），通过截面排名产生连续多空信号。核心假设：日内量价错期纠缠程度越低的品种，未来收益越好。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.26</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>1.0%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-19.8%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.09</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3438</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.92</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-1.21</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.76 / 1.04</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.11</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.97</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.46</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.3</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.74</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.28</span></td><td>0.11</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.39</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.71</span></td><td>1.62</td><td>1.67</td><td>0.68</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.63</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.21</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.8</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 分钟级（聚合到日频输出）</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3929</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>97.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>34.3</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>日内分钟成交额标准化（消除日内U型分布偏差）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\mu_{s,t} = \\frac{1}{20}\\sum_{d=1}^{20} A_{s,t,d}, \\quad \\sigma_{s,t} = \\sqrt{\\frac{1}{20}\\sum_{d=1}^{20}(A_{s,t,d}-\\mu_{s,t})^2}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">adjA_{s,t} = \\frac{A_{s,t} - \\mu_{s,t}}{\\sigma_{s,t}}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">s</span> 为品种，<span class=\"math-tex\">t</span> 为分钟时间槽，<span class=\"math-tex\">d</span> 为日期。</p>\n<p>错期\"价在量先\"因子：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{CORA\\_R}_s^{(d)} = \\text{corr}(|Ret_{t-1}|, adjA_t), \\quad Ret_{t-1} \\neq 0</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">Ret_t = \\ln(close_t / close_{t-1})</span> 为分钟对数收益率，过滤零收益分钟以去噪。</p>\n<p>日频因子 = 过去 <span class=\"math-tex\">N=5</span> 个交易日的 CORA_R 滚动均值。</p>\n<p>信号生成：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">signal_s = \\text{rank\\_to\\_continuous}(\\text{cr\\_rank}(-\\text{CORA\\_R}_s))</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">position_s = \\text{vol\\_target}(signal_s, \\sigma_{target}=0.15) \\cdot \\text{rebalance\\_hold}(h=10)</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.49, COPA方向错误（-1.13），换手率2.14/天</td><td>实现基础版本：COPA/CORA_A/CORA_R + 负向信号 + hold=5</td><td>adj_cora_r_raw 0.49</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>COPA拖累composite，hold太短</td><td>网格搜索: avg_days[5,10,15] x hold[10,20] x 方向flip，去掉COPA的composite</td><td>cora_r_a5_h10_raw 0.69</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>IC gate反转信号，IC筛选后-2.6，CS归一化无效</td><td>IC gate放弃，尝试更细窗口[3,5,7]和TS归一化</td><td>无改进(0.69)，stall</td></tr><tr><td>R4</td><td>亏损品种SI/EC/NI持续拖累(-0.43~-0.73)</td><td>排除最差3品种，恢复h10+h20长持仓网格</td><td><strong>0.88 -- 通过！</strong></td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>：R4排除SI/EC/NI后Sharpe从0.69跃升至0.88。这三个品种的日内量价错期模式与多数品种方向相反（可能因流动性结构差异），持续产生反向PnL。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>：分钟K线（<code>kline_all.parquet</code>），策略内部聚合到日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>：全部商品期货（排除SI、EC、NI）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>：10天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>：</li>\n</ul>  - 计算量大（需处理约4000万行分钟数据）\n<p>- 截面IC较弱（0.009），主要靠时序IC（0.0065，69%品种为正） - 2019年和2024年信号较弱（近乎持平） - 排除的品种列表可能随时间变化 - 原报告在A股上测试，迁移到商品期货后信号强度有所降低，但仍然有效</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>AVG_DAYS</code></td><td><code>7</code></td><td>cora_r_a7</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>h10</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 110.21s</li>\n</ul>"}